'''Eʋegbe''' nye [[Amewo Eʋe|Eʋeawo]] ƒe gbe gbɔgblɔ. Wo dona Eʋegbe le [[Gana]] kpakple [[Togo]] dukɔwo siwo le [[Afrika]] ƒe ɣetoɖoƒe lɔƒo la me. Gbe gbɔgblɔ siwo teɖe Eʋegbe ŋu wonye [[Foŋgbe]] kpakple [[Adzágbe]]. Esiawo katã wonye [[Gbe]] gbewo.

Germania ŋutsu [[:en:Diedrich Hermann Westermann|Diedrich Hermann Westermann]], si srɔ̃ nugeɖe le Afrika ŋuti la, ŋlɔ agbalẽwo geɖe le Eʋegbe ŋuti. Ame bubu siwo srɔ̃ nu le Eʋegbe ŋuti wonye [[Gilbert Ansre]], [[Hounkpati B. Capo]], [[Herbert Stahlke]], [[Roberto Pazzi]], [[Felix K. Ameka]], [[Alan Stewart Duthie]].

== Eʋenyigba ==
Eʋenyigba de lolo ge abe [[Asãte]] kple [[Dahome]], siwo le eƒe goawo kple eve dzi, ene. Ke Eʋeawo katã meƒo ƒu ɖekae wɔ fiaduƒe gã abe woamawo ene kpɔ o .

Togbɔ be ɖekawɔwɔ blibo mele wo dome o hã la, fiaɖufe gã eve mawo dometɔ aɖeke meɖu wo dzi kpɔ o, ke boŋ Eʋeawo nɔ wo ɖokui si, va se ɖe esime yevunya va .

